assets/steam/apps/2376970/extras/6e8c41e0c1bb8c8c3dfa568666433cfe.webm?t=1765377087\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2376970/extras/6e8c41e0c1bb8c8c3dfa568666433cfe.mp4?t=1765377087\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Prove yourself in various competitions</strong></h2>Do you think the bond with your horse is strong enough to win competitions? The more trust there is between the two of you, the more easily your horse will learn new skills and the less afraid they will be of new challenges.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2376970/extras/d6bd7b4ad5a6f989b0ab105205481d7f.poster.avif?t=1765377087\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2376970/extras/d6bd7b4ad5a6f989b0ab105205481d7f.webm?t=1765377087\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2376970/extras/d6bd7b4ad5a6f989b0ab105205481d7f.mp4?t=1765377087\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
